## 🔧 Code Refactoring

### CR-001: Centralize Theme Colors & Use CSS Variables
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🔴 Critical
- **Files**: `src/contexts/ThemeContext.tsx`, `src/constants/themes.ts`, `src/components/BankDashboard.tsx`
