## ⚡ Performance

### PERF-001: Implement Code Splitting with React.lazy
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🔴 Critical
- **Files**: `src/App.tsx`
- **Issue**: All 12+ major views (TodayView, SafeView, BankDashboard, etc.) are imported synchronously, bloating the initial bundle size.
- **Solution**: Use `React.lazy()` and `<Suspense>` for route-based code splitting
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-11
- **Notes**: Lazy loaded 13 views: TodayView, TasksAndEventsView, JournalView, AnalyticsView, SettingsView, ItemsView, SafeView, TimerView, ResolutionsView, TodoView, SmartView, GroupsManager, VoiceCommandHistory. Added ViewLoader fallback component.

### PERF-002: Lazy Load Recharts Library
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🔴 Critical
- **Files**: `src/App.tsx`, `src/SafeView.tsx`
- **Issue**: Recharts (PieChart, BarChart, AreaChart) imported at module level. 3,800+ line component loads even if user never visits dashboard.
- **Solution**: Dynamically import recharts or lazy load entire BankDashboard
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-11
- **Notes**: BankDashboard lazy loaded in both App.tsx and SafeView.tsx with dedicated Suspense fallback. Recharts now only loads when user accesses Financial Dashboard.

### PERF-003: Fix N+1 Query Pattern in SafeEntryList
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🔴 Critical
- **Files**: `src/components/SafeEntryList.tsx`
- **Issue**: Sequential API calls in loop - for each entry, makes separate `getUnresolvedCommentCount()` call. 50 entries = 50 API calls.
- **Solution**: Batch into single query `getUnresolvedCommentCountsBatch(entryIds)` or use `Promise.all()` for parallel execution
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-11
- **Notes**: Changed from sequential for-loop to `Promise.all()` for parallel execution. All comment counts now fetched simultaneously instead of one-by-one.

### PERF-004: Add React.memo to List Components
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🟡 Medium
- **Files**: `SafeEntryList.tsx`, `TodayView.tsx`, `TodoView.tsx`, `TasksAndEventsView.tsx`
- **Issue**: No components use `React.memo()`. Child components re-render unnecessarily when parent state changes.
- **Solution**: Created memoized SafeEntryCard component; added memo imports to key views
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-11
- **Notes**: Extracted SafeEntryCard as memoized component reducing re-renders when list changes

### PERF-005: Add Input Debouncing
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🟡 Medium
- **Files**: `src/hooks/useDebounce.ts`, `src/components/SafeEntryList.tsx`, `src/components/SettingsModal.tsx`
- **Issue**: No debounce/throttle. Search inputs trigger filtering on every keystroke.
- **Solution**: Created reusable useDebounce/useDebouncedCallback/useThrottledCallback hooks; applied to search inputs
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-11
- **Notes**: Hook includes value debounce and callback debounce/throttle utilities

### PERF-006: Implement List Virtualization
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🟡 Medium
- **Files**: `src/hooks/useVirtualList.ts`
- **Issue**: Lists render all DOM nodes regardless of viewport visibility. Performance degrades with 50+ items.
- **Solution**: Created reusable `useVirtualList` hook with configurable item height, overscan, and auto-threshold (30+ items)
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-12
- **Notes**: Lightweight hook without external dependencies; supports scroll-to-index and dynamic enable/disable

### PERF-007: Memoize Filter/Map Chains
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🟡 Medium
- **Files**: `src/components/BankDashboard.tsx`, `src/components/SafeEntryForm.tsx`
- **Issue**: Chained `.filter().map()` creates multiple intermediate arrays on every render.
- **Solution**: Wrapped key derived data with `useMemo()` - deposits filtering, bank totals, pie data, tag categories
