- **Notes**: BankDashboard: upcoming90, sortedDeps, bankTotals, pieData memoized; SafeEntryForm: categoryTags, regularTags memoized

### PERF-008: Optimize TOTP Refresh Interval
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🟢 Low
- **Files**: `src/components/SafeEntryDetail.tsx`
- **Issue**: 1-second interval for TOTP code refresh runs even when TOTP isn't displayed or entry has no TOTP secret.
- **Solution**: Now regenerates TOTP code only when 30s time window changes; countdown still updates every second
- **Completed Date**: 2026-03-12
- **Notes**: Reduced expensive crypto operations from 1/sec to 1/30sec per entry Minor CPU optimization

### PERF-009: Add Lazy Loading to Images
- **Status**: ✅ Completed
- **Priority**: 🟢 Low
- **Files**: `src/components/WeatherWidget.tsx`
- **Issue**: Weather icon images load eagerly without `loading="lazy"` attribute.
- **Solution**: Added `loading="lazy"` to all 3 weather icon img tags
